<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Week 2: Bootstrap Layout</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Custom styles to make the grid visible */
        .header, .footer { background-color: #343a40; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .sidebar { background-color: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; min-height: 200px; padding: 15px; }
        .main-content { background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; min-height: 200px; padding: 15px; }
        .box { padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 1px dashed #6c757d; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header mb-3">
        <h1>Karthik's Bootstrap Site</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-3">
            
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-12">
                <div class="sidebar">
                    <h4>Menu</h4>
                    <ul class="nav flex-column">
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Home</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">About</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Contact</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer mt-3">
        <p>CMR Institute of Technology | FSD Lab</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
